<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>{% block title %}BarberShop!{% endblock %}</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css"
          integrity="sha384-ggOyR0iXCbMQv3Xipma34MD+dH/1fQ784/j6cY/iJTQUOhcWr7x9JvoRxT2MZw1T" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/css/style.css">
</head>
<body style="width: 700px;">
<div class="color-jumbotron-home jumbotron text-center text-white rounded-0 p-0"
     style="background-color: #000000; height: 130px;">
    <div class="row m-0">
        <div class="col-12" style="padding: 30px 0">
            <h1 class="title-h1">BarberShop</h1>
            <p class="description">Réinisialisation de votre mot de passe</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="text-center">
    <p style="font-size: 18px;">
        <strong style="color: #d92139; font-size: 15px;">
            {{ user.username }}</strong>
        tu as oublié ton mot de passe, tu vas pouvoir le réinisialiser en cliquant sur ce lien :</p>
    <p style="font-size: 20px;">
        <a href="{{ url }}"><strong>Barbershop</strong></a>
    </p>
</div>
</body>
</html>